{"word":"Rome","slug":"rome","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Rome</b> <a href=\"#/G4516\">G4516</a> <br/> The capital of the Roman empire.<br/> Jews excluded from, by Claudius<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=18&verse=2'>Act 18:2</a><br/> Paul's visit to<br/> <a href='S:Paul'>Paul</a><br/> Visited by Onesiphorus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=55&chapter=1&verse=17'>2Ti 1:17</a><br/> Paul desires to preach in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=1&verse=15'>Rom 1:15</a><br/> Abominations in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=1&verse=32'>Rom 1:32</a><br/> Christians in:<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=16&verse=17'>Rom 16:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=50&chapter=1&verse=18'>Phi 1:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=50&chapter=4&verse=22'>Phi 4:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=55&chapter=4&verse=21'>2Ti 4:21</a><br/> Paul's letter to the Christians in<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=1&verse=7'>Rom 1:7</a> <br/> - The gospel of Christ<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=1&verse=16'>Rom 1:16</a> <br/> - The condemnation of the Gentiles<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=1&verse=18'>Rom 1:18</a> <br/> - The condemnation of the Jews<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=2'>Rom 2</a> <br/> - God's judgment against all sin<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=2&verse=6'>Rom 2:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=3'>Rom 3</a> <br/> - Justification by faith in Jesus Christ<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=3&verse=24'>Rom 3:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=4'>Rom 4</a> <br/> - The faith of Abraham<br/